				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13860978/scp-5506#post-4831005</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 29 Nov 2020 07:19:44 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Grigori Karpin</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4558017</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I love the tone of this article most of all. The overly serious, super evil entity and its megalomaniac speech are so EDGY scary, grimdark&#8230; but its mode of infecting reality is just RIDICULOUS.</p> <p>This is what the best satire is made of: Deadly serious tone, but the subject matter is laughable. The secret, which this article does brilliantly, is that no one in universe is realizing how silly this all is. But we, as the reader, can tell because the situation just keeps escalating in silly ways.</p> <p>+1 if only for the gory scenes caused by consumption of coffee and the ridiculous conprocs. Anytime you two work together, I know I am in for an excellent ride.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
