				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13860978#post-4818202</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13860978/scp-5506#post-4818202</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 14 Nov 2020 09:51:57 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>WizzBlizz</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>6760712</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>and to popularize the exploitation of workers employed in all aspects of the coffee industry.</p> </blockquote> <p>How is this supposed to reduce coffee consumption? This would just make coffee production more efficient and profitable.</p> <p>And I don't think the popularization of worker exploitation would require some kind of outside influence.</p> <p>I would replace this with:</p> <blockquote> <p>and to drastically increase media coverage and popular consciousness of worker exploitation in the coffee industry.</p> </blockquote> <p>Something like that would make more sense.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
