					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="border:solid 1px #000000; color:#000000; border-radius: 10px; background:#752d00; padding:5px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding:10px"> <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><span style="font-size:125%;"><strong><em>“Black as night, sweet as sin.”</em></strong></span></p> </div> <br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;&#32;</span>― Neil Gaiman, <em>Anansi Boys</em></div> <br /> Here's another piping hot cup o' Donk/Graves for your enjoyment. As always, it's an incredible pleasure to work with <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255688&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1605292393" alt="DrAkimoto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255688)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drakimoto" >DrAkimoto</a></span>, one that I deeply cherish and appreciate. Thank you, friend. You're the best. <p>Special thanks to our critters: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-fullham" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1989312&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1605292393" alt="Doctor Fullham" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1989312)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-fullham" >Doctor Fullham</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ocuin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot